y_speed_profile()</code> 的 <code>default /* 5 fastest */</code> 分支及位图循环相关逻辑：</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>项</th><th>数值</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>inter_group_us</code></td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td><code>line_cooling_us</code></td><td>10</td></tr><tr><td><code>heat_us_at_5c / 25c / 40c</code></td><td>1080 / 940 / 820</td></tr><tr><td><code>motor_step_us</code></td><td>650</td></tr><tr><td><code>status_check_period_lines</code></td><td>96</td></tr><tr><td>连续白行批量上限</td><td>96</td></tr><tr><td>周期性 <code>rt_thread_mdelay(1)</code></td><td>约每 256 行</td></tr><tr><td>位图结束后 <code>thermal_printer_feed</code></td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>高密度行额外加热（黑点档）</td><td>+135 / +90 / +55 / +28 / +10（分档）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"与组一的差异便于分析\">与组一的差异（便于分析）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#与组一的差异便于分析\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>纸上多出 <strong>Modes 文本块</strong>（由 <code>thermal_printer_print_text</code> → 内部再走位图，会略增加总时长与走纸，属正常现象）。  </li>\n<li>热参数与白行批量相对组一<strong>更激进</strong>，同图下 <code>C</code> 通常应 ≤ 组一；若画质下降，可对照两组样张与参数表回调。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"归档建议\">归档建议<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#归档建议\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>文件名建议：<code>YYYYMMDD_纸上Modes行首模式名_含Modes_备注.jpg</code>（与 <code>* </code> 行一致即可）。</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI ��ӡ���̼��ĵ���","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"801bb942f5d3a833cb045cb9b3abd9d0","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":96},"end":{"line":8,"column":28,"offset":121},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�"}},{"type":"wiki","f